{"image_id": "LH_2006_page_45", "image_size": [1238, 1725], "ocr": [{"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS", "bbox": [110.5, 179.0, 821.5, 216.5]}, {"text": "(Dollars and shares in millions, except per share data)", "bbox": [110.5, 225.7, 515.4, 246.5]}, {"text": "Laboratory Corporation of America", "bbox": [820.5, 1662.4, 1049.4, 1681.2]}, {"text": "® Holdings 2006  43", "bbox": [1049.4, 1662.4, 1185.9, 1681.2]}, {"text": "............................... ........", "bbox": [76.9, 88.3, 105.0, 406.3]}, {"text": ".......................................", "bbox": [22.9, 135.3, 331.6, 163.4]}, {"text": "On December 7, 2005, the Company executed an overnight share", "bbox": [152.1, 287.4, 632.3, 308.3]}, {"text": "repurchase transaction with a bank for the acquisition of 4.8 shares", "bbox": [114.6, 316.6, 613.2, 337.4]}, {"text": "of the Company’s outstanding common stock for an initial purchase", "bbox": [114.6, 345.8, 612.7, 366.6]}, {"text": "price of $52.04 per share. The transaction was financed with borrowings", "bbox": [114.6, 374.9, 632.0, 395.8]}, {"text": "under the Company’s revolving line of credit. The Company used cash", "bbox": [114.6, 404.1, 630.2, 424.9]}, {"text": "on hand and the proceeds of the Senior Notes due 2015 to repay", "bbox": [114.6, 433.3, 596.7, 454.1]}, {"text": "borrowings under the Company’s revolving credit facility. Pursuant to", "bbox": [114.6, 462.4, 622.3, 483.3]}, {"text": "the agreement with the bank, the bank purchased 4.8 shares in the open", "bbox": [114.6, 491.6, 630.1, 512.4]}, {"text": "market over the period ended June 13, 2006. At the end of the purchase", "bbox": [114.6, 520.8, 632.3, 541.6]}, {"text": "period, the Company made a cash payment of $22.9 to the bank to settle", "bbox": [114.6, 549.9, 631.2, 570.8]}, {"text": "its obligation for the purchase price adjustment based on the volume", "bbox": [114.6, 579.1, 619.9, 599.9]}, {"text": "weighted-average purchase price of the shares acquired compared", "bbox": [114.6, 608.3, 610.6, 629.1]}, {"text": "to the initial purchase price. The total cost of the initial purchase was", "bbox": [114.6, 637.4, 617.6, 658.3]}, {"text": "approximately $251.7, including a $1.5 cap premium and $0.2 in", "bbox": [114.6, 666.6, 600.3, 687.4]}, {"text": "commissions and other fees. The shares repurchased under the", "bbox": [114.6, 695.8, 586.7, 716.6]}, {"text": "overnight share repurchase agreement were immediately canceled", "bbox": [114.6, 724.9, 607.7, 745.8]}, {"text": "and returned to the status of authorized but unissued shares. The", "bbox": [114.6, 754.1, 596.8, 774.9]}, {"text": "Company reduced common stock and additional paid in capital by", "bbox": [114.6, 783.3, 599.9, 804.1]}, {"text": "approximately $0.5 and $251.2, respectively to record the initial", "bbox": [114.6, 812.4, 589.3, 833.3]}, {"text": "purchase price. The forward contract associated with the overnight", "bbox": [114.6, 841.6, 607.8, 862.4]}, {"text": "share repurchase transaction was accounted for in accordance with", "bbox": [114.6, 870.8, 614.7, 891.6]}, {"text": "EITF 00-19 as an equity instrument. The $22.9 paid in connection", "bbox": [114.6, 899.9, 602.6, 920.8]}, {"text": "with the price adjustment was recorded as a reduction to additional", "bbox": [114.6, 929.1, 610.2, 949.9]}, {"text": "paid in capital. The diluted net income per share calculation for the", "bbox": [114.6, 958.3, 606.5, 979.1]}, {"text": "year ended December 31, 2006 includes the potential shares of", "bbox": [114.6, 987.4, 592.4, 1008.3]}, {"text": "common stock that could have been issued to settle the overnight", "bbox": [114.6, 1016.6, 598.9, 1037.4]}, {"text": "share repurchase transaction.", "bbox": [114.6, 1045.8, 338.5, 1066.6]}, {"text": "Stockholder Rights Plan", "bbox": [114.6, 1103.9, 304.6, 1124.8]}, {"text": "The Company adopted a stockholder rights plan effective as of", "bbox": [114.6, 1133.3, 574.9, 1154.1]}, {"text": "December 13, 2001 that provides that each common stockholder", "bbox": [114.6, 1162.4, 598.8, 1183.3]}, {"text": "of record on December 21, 2001 received a dividend of one right", "bbox": [114.6, 1191.6, 594.9, 1212.4]}, {"text": "for each share of common stock held. Each right entitles the holder", "bbox": [114.6, 1220.8, 609.4, 1241.6]}, {"text": "to purchase from the Company one-hundredth of a share of a new", "bbox": [114.6, 1249.9, 603.3, 1270.8]}, {"text": "series of participating preferred stock at an initial purchase price of", "bbox": [114.6, 1279.1, 607.8, 1299.9]}, {"text": "four hundred dollars. These rights will become exercisable and will", "bbox": [114.6, 1308.3, 605.5, 1329.1]}, {"text": "detach from the Company’s common stock if any person becomes", "bbox": [114.6, 1337.4, 606.5, 1358.3]}, {"text": "the beneficial owner of 15% or more of the Company’s common", "bbox": [114.6, 1366.6, 588.0, 1387.4]}, {"text": "stock. In that event, each right will entitle the holder, other than the", "bbox": [114.6, 1395.8, 608.3, 1416.6]}, {"text": "acquiring person, to purchase, for the initial purchase price, shares", "bbox": [114.6, 1424.9, 609.5, 1445.8]}, {"text": "of the Company’s common stock having a value of twice the initial", "bbox": [114.6, 1454.1, 601.2, 1474.9]}, {"text": "purchase price. The rights will expire on December 13, 2011, unless", "bbox": [114.6, 1483.3, 610.9, 1504.1]}, {"text": "earlier exchanged or redeemed.", "bbox": [114.6, 1512.4, 347.7, 1533.2]}, {"text": "Accumulated Other Comprehensive Earnings", "bbox": [652.4, 287.0, 1007.7, 307.8]}, {"text": "The components of accumulated other comprehensive earnings are", "bbox": [652.4, 316.3, 1151.1, 337.2]}, {"text": "as follows:", "bbox": [652.4, 345.5, 734.8, 366.3]}, {"text": "Foreign", "bbox": [822.2, 388.4, 870.0, 405.1]}, {"text": "Minimum", "bbox": [910.3, 388.4, 969.5, 405.1]}, {"text": "Adoption of", "bbox": [993.8, 388.4, 1065.2, 405.1]}, {"text": "Accumulated", "bbox": [1080.8, 388.4, 1157.7, 405.1]}, {"text": "Currency